Package data

Class Worker

java.lang.Object
data.Worker
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable<Worker>
public class Worker extends Object implements Comparable<Worker>
Represents a worker with a unique ID, name, coordinates, creation date, salary, position, status, and personal information. Implements the Comparable interface for comparing workers based on salary.
